text: He sarva milunahi tumacyasi ladhu sakata nahi, matra hi gosta vegali ki killyane gheralelya thikani asaveta kinva bhintincya adosala asaveta. Tyanci ladha'i tara apasataca mothi sakta ahe. Jari tumhi tyanna ekasangha samajata ahata tari, vastutah tyanci mane apasata vibhakta aheta he asasathi ki he nirbud'dha loka aheta
